/src/
│
├── nija_app.py              ← main live Flask app + background trading worker
├── nija_write_pem.py        ← writes your COINBASE_PEM_CONTENT secret into a .pem file
├── nija_client.py           ← handles Coinbase authentication + balance/trade functions
├── trading_logic.py         ← your buy/sell decision logic (optional, can expand)
│
├── requirements.txt         ← includes cdp-sdk, flask, gunicorn, etc.
├── nija_preflight.py        ← quick pre-check for JWT + credentials (optional)
│
├── __init__.py              ← (optional) can be empty, helps Python treat folder as a module
│
└── Procfile                 ← tells Render how to start the app
